<p class="prayer">The grace of our Lord Jesus Christ, and the love of God, and the fellowship of the Holy Spirit, be with us all evermore. Amen.</p>
<p class="reference">2 Corinthians 13:14</p>
<p class="prayer">May the God of hope fill us with all joy and peace in believing through the power of the Holy Spirit. Amen.</p>
<p class="reference">Romans 15:13</p>
<p class="prayer">Glory to God whose power, working in us, can do infinitely more than we can ask or imagine: Glory to him from generation to generation in the Church, and in Christ Jesus forever and ever. Amen.</p>
